[[Emerging technologies]] are those technical innovations which represent progressive developments within a field for [[competition (economics)|competitive advantage]].<ref>International Congress Innovation and Technology XXI: Strategies and Policies Towards the XXI Century, & Soares, O. D. D. (1997). Innovation and technology: Strategies and policies. Dordrecht: Kluwer Academic.</ref>
